<template>
<svg width="90" height="60" viewBox="0 0 90 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="empty-pie-svg">
<g>
    <circle cx="45" cy="35" r="20" fill="#A0C4FF" opacity="0.25" />
    <path class="pie-slice slice1" d="M45,35 L65,35 A20,20 0 0,0 45,15 Z" fill="#4F8EF7" />
    <path class="pie-slice slice2" d="M45,35 L45,15 A20,20 0 1,0 65,35 Z" fill="#FFB300" />
</g>
</svg>
</template>

<script setup>
</script>

<style scoped>
.empty-pie-svg {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: floatX 3.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.pie-slice {
    transform-origin: 45px 35px;
    opacity: 0.85;
    animation: pie-pop 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) infinite alternate;
}
.slice1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.slice2 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
@keyframes pie-pop {
    0% { transform: scale(0.7); opacity: 0.5; }
    60% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scale(0.7); opacity: 0.5; }
}
@keyframes floatX {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    25% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) translateX(-4px); }
    75% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
}
</style>
